title: Firmware  for pgt(4) and bwi(4) in OpenBSD
tags:
  - openbsd
id: 508
categories:
  - Software
date: 2010-03-23 03:18:27
---

[OpenBSD](http://www.openbsd.org) does not provide closed firmware in their installation sets; You must manually install the required firmware packages. As root:`
# pkg_add -ivvv http://www.nazgul.ch/bwi/bwi-firmware-1.4.tgz
# pkg_add -ivvv http://www.nazgul.ch/pgt/pgt-firmware-1.2.tgz`